/// Social Determinants of Health dimension keyed by ZIP code. Community-level measures (poverty rate, food desert, transportation, housing instability, uninsured rate, broadband access, median income) plus a composite social_vulnerability_index and risk_tier. Join to dim_patient on zip_code.
